00:35:16.240 --> 00:35:19.190
You're not American.

00:35:19.190 --> 00:35:23.570
- As a woman creator, the idea
that maybe my stories would

00:35:23.570 --> 00:35:28.370
naturally be romance stories
or soap-opera-type stories.

00:35:28.370 --> 00:35:31.640
In reality, I like
big adventure stories

00:35:31.640 --> 00:35:35.780
