00:35:47.284 --> 00:35:49.200
There's a lot of people
who have had hardships

00:35:49.200 --> 00:35:50.610
before Sikhs came here.

00:35:50.610 --> 00:35:52.410
Get out of your
comfort zone, which

00:35:52.410 --> 00:35:55.590
means do things that haven't
been done by a community

00:35:55.590 --> 00:35:56.942
before.

00:35:56.942 --> 00:35:59.347
