00:36:11.920 --> 00:36:15.600
which is make stories
from my perspective,

00:36:15.600 --> 00:36:21.210
showing that I am more than
what is depicted in mainstream

00:36:21.210 --> 00:36:25.860
media, then we can really
have a decent discussion

00:36:25.860 --> 00:36:30.840
about solving the problems and
issues of race and stereotypes.

